<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css" />
    <style>

        .about-hero {
            background-color: var(--gray-light);
            padding: 4rem 2rem;
            display: flex; /* Use flexbox */
            align-items: center; /* Center vertically */
            justify-content: center; /* Center horizontally */
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 12px;
            flex-direction: column; /* Stack content vertically */
        }
      .about-hero h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        color: var(--primary-blue);
      }

      .about-hero p {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        color: var(--text);
        margin-top: 1rem;
        opacity: 0.8;
      }

      .team {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 4rem 0;
      }

      .team h2 {
        font-size: 2rem;
        color: var(--text);
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }
    </style>
    <title>About Us</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">

      <header class="hero about-hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
          <h1>About Us</h1>
        </div>
      </header>

      <section class="features">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>Who we are ?</h3>
          <p>
            We are a dedicated team of students from Gebze Technical University,
            creating innovative solutions in the field of pharmacy and
            healthcare. With diverse backgrounds in software development,
            project management, and product design, we collaborate to provide
            impactful tools for the pharmaceutical industry.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>What is our purpose ?</h3>
          <p>
            Our goal is to develop a user-friendly, efficient, and secure
            web-based stock management system tailored specifically for pharmacy
            warehouses. By streamlining inventory processes and improving stock
            visibility, we aim to empower pharmacies with the tools they need to
            optimize operations and ensure the availability of essential
            medicines.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="team">
        <h2>Meet Our Team</h2>
        <div class="features">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon"></div>
            <h3>Ahmet Sadri Güler</h3>
            <p>Product Owner</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon"></div>
            <h3>Soner Güneş</h3>
            <p>Project Manager</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon"></div>
            <h3>Ünal Sarıemir</h3>
            <p>Developer</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon"></div>
            <h3>Hüseyin Çetin</h3>
            <p>Developer</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon"></div>
            <h3>Yavuz Selman Haltaş</h3>
            <p>Developer</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>